title: 10 Medical Books (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 medical books in true PDF format. If you have trouble reading any of them in Adobe reader, then use a better reader like Foxit or Sumatra:

01. Biostatistics - A Computing Approach
02. Cardiovascular and Metabolic Disease - Scientific Discoveries and New Therapies
03. Clinical Guide to Helping New Parents - The Couple CARE for Parents Program1
04. Hepatobiliary Medicine - Self-Assessment Colour Review
05. Lupus - The Essential Clinician's Guide (2nd Ed)
06. Medical Imaging Technology - Reviews and Computational Applications
07. Otitis Media - State of the Art Concepts and Treatment
08. Reducing Mortality in Critically Ill Patients1
09. Sports Injuries and Prevention
10. Trauma and Migration - Cultural Factors in the Diagnosis and Treatment of Traumatised Immigrants
